I also have the 3-bulb florescent lamp (CDN model).

I took a peek behind the dash. It looks like the silver socket is wired to
terminal 30 on the hazard switch (un-fused) by 16 awg wire. Would 100W be
safe then? It seems most of the motorcycle clothing max. out at 50W.

I searched the archives and Steve Dolan suggested using an existing cut-out
in the dash to putin a US lighter socket. I checked and I can see it but the
hole needs to be widened.

